name: Moshi Monsters Katsuma Unleashed
description: Fur will Fly! Help Katsuma defeat his arch enemies, including an army of robot Moshlings and an epic showdown with the dastardly Dr.Strangeglove! A Monster Journey - Jump and dash your way though 6 new worlds jam-packed with multiple levels and hidden secrets! Super Moshi Abilities - Rescue your Moshi friends and obtain amazing new abilities that unlock exciting short-cuts and fun new areas for you to explore. Play Mini Games - Play exclusive mini-games and achieve high scores that unlock super items!
